{"h73049fc0g1b01g4a04ga998g91e6903bd5c4": ["*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead.html", "efa1e4c4-b790-9e7b-c673-0187d583acce"], "h49bda94cg87b1g4657g8e93g2ec9de421fc0": ["*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead.html", "4f5996ef-8556-0844-8c22-efa0f66de951"], "h113ce312g85cfg4a21gbdecg747fdacac479": ["*The corpse regards you lifelessly.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead.html", "7a732b51-acd1-eeba-5db6-912e2198f879"], "h979f2dafg4e27g497fg97f3g5315f3d47dff": ["Urgh... <i>cold</i>...", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead.html", "8d4bf0e6-613f-0f8d-5c16-c6ca8fdcdc36"], "h869c49fegc919g4ab8g9890g240076611ccf": ["Who are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead.html", "89f70d10-4200-4959-5a47-890be8b8c4f7"], "hb7fbc59fgdc8ag40d0ga578g8d10af8b359a": ["Fezzerk... best raider... east o' the... Sea o' Swords...", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead.html", "18fd40d4-4151-030c-c2fc-11a47032eb4f"], "h2e8d8029gd6c7g4d12g84e8ge8c65a2f6207": ["What were you doing in the village?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead.html", "0e5393ff-cf03-d861-78a9-977fb5ebdd1b"], "h34db8b31gf91cg4b5egafdagbe4554003e14": ["Hostages... the Absolute wants... <i>hostages</i>...", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead.html", "5096e1ec-4c78-f8ca-e1d9-ff1a922de234"], "h6064ae9fgfed2g4f67gac13g3fca6fedea94": ["Did you have any valuables?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead.html", "defdd00b-4b6d-e262-0308-d02be74c48b9"], "h54c41d5dgcf8cg40bbgaa3ag3a0b154411df": ["No... valuables... only... hostages...", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead.html", "a2f9ff1a-3f37-6887-7a27-7cf2a9826f07"], "h4769a791g4785g46d4g852ag2d404da25175": ["Who killed you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead.html", "98942712-a782-9fb1-e789-1bb7cbedf9b0"], "h7c0a20ccg2473g439cga3b2gb2b568a36fb2": ["Coward... attacked...  interrupted my work... ", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead.html", "a3b5d265-6a63-25ae-a5a3-35ca625f6bd9"], "h43b9e19cg2456g4997g9f21gf1c186967b08": ["Where did you come from?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead.html", "3210ab92-3f9a-7035-9e48-c22138f4504b"], "hf06b8137gcbdfg4061ga3d3g744268020b72": ["The... <i>towers...</i>", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead.html", "caf3fb27-4294-4dde-d219-a2d67b0afcbf"], "he6d8ed0cg5192g40deg803eg05be9ea0bf27": ["Who did you answer to?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead.html", "cfbb8a33-f056-0d16-1a57-3f0c3ed619ec"], "hd3b7c33agfe0bg451ega64dg290c9589f760": ["The... Absolute... she... chose us...", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead.html", "ad80bca7-8acd-75be-a299-3363e6bd9cc4"], "hca1c19dagc928g4733g93d1g8a684e599e2d": ["Are there others like you nearby?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead.html", "1a55665d-6c83-6ab5-b549-3c30d1e6d08a"], "h11c2fd76g2de7g41a2gae68g1b8c22a3912d": ["Many... so many... legions o' goblins... an' more... serving... the Absolute...", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead.html", "37bd0e52-ff19-45d0-3691-6f5e4593b11d"], "h3464d1aeg4629g4709g9308g451cfa2e5b86": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead.html", "b35303bf-228d-116f-dfb9-221bd558f831"], "he8f80629gdfc2g49c8gb311g515fde27160c": ["*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead.html", "c75aa411-0cde-7305-d135-aeb1671e9a2d"]}